HEADWORD: Vermifuge
<hw>Ver"mi*fuge</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>vermifuge</ets>. See <er>Vermifugal</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A medicine or substance that expels worms from animal bodies; an
anthelmintic.</def>⟦br⟧
